@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_oktbet(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = (wp.abs(wp.cos(v1 + 0.56)) * 0.90)
    v1 = (v2 - wp.abs((tmp + 0.45 + v2 + 0.73)))
    v0 = ((0.14 * wp.cos(v2 + 0.78)) * (wp.cos(tmp + 0.48) / (v1 + 0.89 - v0 + 0.53)))
    tmp = wp.sin(0.15)
    v2 = wp.cos(tmp)
    v0 = (wp.cos((v2 + 0.47 + tmp + 0.66)) * 0.51)
    tmp = 0.15
    data[tid] = v0
